                        <li><strong>Digital Nomads:</strong> Remote workers exploring Toronto for 1-3 months at a time</li>
                        <li><strong>Film & TV Production:</strong> Toronto's booming film industry brings cast and crew needing monthly housing</li>
                        <li><strong>University Visitors:</strong> Visiting professors, researchers, and graduate students</li>
                        <li><strong>New Immigrants:</strong> Newcomers to Canada needing temporary furnished housing while they settle</li>
